Trade/Device Name(s): IMMULITE Unconjugated Estriol (uE3) Calibration Verification Material
IMMULITE® Unconjugated Estriol (uE3) Calibration Verification Material
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for IMMULITE Unconjugated Estriol (uE3) Calibration Verification Material used for calibration verification of IMMULITE uE3 assays on IMMULITE platforms.
Indications for Use Summary: For in vitro diagnostic use as a control for calibration verification of IMMULITE Unconjugated Estriol (uE3) assays on the IMMULITE, IMMULITE 1000, and IMMULITE 2000 systems.
